text: The Cock-Eyed World is a 1929 American musical comedy movie directed by Raoul Walsh and is the sequel to What Price Glory?. It stars Victor McLaglen, Edmund Lowe, Lili Damita, El Brendel and was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1929 comedy movies Category:1920s musical movies Category:American musical comedy movies Category:American sequel movies Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies directed by Raoul Walsh
title: The Cock-Eyed World
